<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="0" /><anim id="Fuming" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哼<tag a="110" b="0" />！<delay frames="60" />
<anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果不想被迁怒的话，<delay20 />
就别靠近我！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="0" /><anim id="Fuming" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊啊～～～！<delay frames="60" />
<anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我这烦躁的心情，<delay8 />
要怎么样发泄才好啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="0" /><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />抱歉，不过暂时别管我！<delay frames="40" />
我想一个人待一会儿！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="100" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="0" /><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />这家伙<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />说到底<delay20 />
也只是个小鬼头嘛！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="0" /><anim id="Outraged" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="100" b="0" /><tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><endTag a="100" b="0" />那家伙<delay8 />
根本一点都不理解
我的感受！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="0" /><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />马耳东风、<delay frames="40" />白费力气、<delay8 />无济于事、<delay8 />对牛弹琴，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Outraged" target="actor" targetSpec="" />用这些词来形容简直再合适不过了！<10_4 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不管对那家伙说什么都是没用的！<anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也不是<delay20 />因为喜欢<delay8 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />才说些大道理的。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只是要给那种不谙世事的家伙<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />讲讲道理而已。<pageBreak /><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />然后你知道<delay20 /><tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />是什么反应吗？<delay frames="60" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我说那么多都是出于好意，<delay20 />
<anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />结果那家伙竟然一口一句“对对对”敷衍了事！
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那种瞧不起人的态度，<delay20 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你也觉得不太好对吧？！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="103_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">也是呢</message>
	<message label="103_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />对对对……</message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />对吧！<delay frames="60" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有人能理解我，<delay8 />
我总算是觉得好受一点了。
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过，<delay8 />我以后<delay8 />
也得稍微克制一点，
不该对别人指手划脚的啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="0" /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />唉<tag a="110" b="0" />
真是<delay8 />受不了啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="200" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="0" /><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />别管我！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我现在不想和你说话。<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="0" /><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我跟你没什么好说的。<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="202" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="0" /><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />别再继续惹我生气了<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="203" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />干什么，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="3" />！<delay frames="60" />
<anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就算现在道歉也太迟了，<delay20 />
闪一边去！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="203_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />抱歉啦</message>
	<message label="203_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />知道了……</message>
	<message label="204" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我知道啦<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="80" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我感受到你的诚意了！<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这次的事情<delay20 />
就既往不咎咯。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="205" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呼<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="80" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看来你也有在反省，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就差不多原谅你了吧。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
